data.name: grdPaList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT DECODE(:f_gubun, '1', A.ORDER_DATE, '2', A.ACTING_DATE, '3', A.RESULT_DATE) QUERY_DATE , A.GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.ORDER_DATE) , A.DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) --, A.PKOCS1003 , 'O' IO_GUBUN , A.BUNHO FROM OCS0103 B , OCS1003 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.RESULT_DATE IS NOT NULL AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND B.RESULT_GUBUN = 'S' AND A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND NVL(B.END_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ORDER_DATE IS NOT NULL) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACTING_DATE IS NOT NULL) OR (:f_gubun = '3') ) UNION SELECT DISTINCT DECODE(:f_gubun, '1', A.ORDER_DATE, '2', A.ACTING_DATE, '3', A.RESULT_DATE) QUERY_DATE , A.INPUT_GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.INPUT_GWA, A.ORDER_DATE) , A.DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) --, A.PKOCS2003 , 'I' IO_GUBUN , A.BUNHO FROM OCS0103 B , OCS2003 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.RESULT_DATE IS NOT NULL AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND B.RESULT_GUBUN = 'S' AND A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND NVL(B.END_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ORDER_DATE IS NOT NULL) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACTING_DATE IS NOT NULL) OR (:f_gubun = '3') ) ORDER BY 1 DESC, 6, 2, 7

data.name: layPKOCS.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.PKOCS1003 FROM OCS0103 B , OCS1003 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.RESULT_DATE IS NOT NULL AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND B.RESULT_GUBUN = 'S' AND A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND NVL(B.END_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ORDER_DATE = :f_date) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACTING_DATE = :f_date) OR (:f_gubun = '3' AND A.RESULT_DATE = :f_date) ) UNION SELECT A.PKOCS2003 FROM OCS0103 B , OCS2003 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.RESULT_DATE IS NOT NULL AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND B.RESULT_GUBUN = 'S' AND A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND NVL(B.END_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ORDER_DATE = :f_date) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACTING_DATE = :f_date) OR (:f_gubun = '3' AND A.RESULT_DATE = :f_date) )

data.name: layMakeTabPage.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT '%' , '%' , FN_ADM_MSG(221) , 1 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.JUNDAL_TABLE_OUT , A.JUNDAL_PART_OUT , B.BUSEO_NAME , 2 FROM OCS0103 A , BAS0260 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = 'XXX' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.JUNDAL_PART_OUT = B.GWA AND B.BUSEO_GUBUN = '3' AND A.RESULT_GUBUN = 'S' UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.JUNDAL_TABLE_INP , A.JUNDAL_PART_INP , B.BUSEO_NAME , 2 FROM OCS0103 A , BAS0260 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = 'XXX' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.JUNDAL_PART_INP = B.GWA AND B.BUSEO_GUBUN = '3' AND A.RESULT_GUBUN = 'S' UNION SELECT 'HOM' , 'HOM' , 'HOM' , 9 FROM DUAL ORDER BY 4 , 1
